snippet.title: Sonic Adventure 2: Super Hard Mode (Hero Pack #1)
snippet.description:
New Super Hard Level Layouts for Sonic Adventure 2! In this video I cover the Hero stages that were released in the super hard stage pack. There are some really clever changes in these stages.
